---
import Layout from '../../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Free AI Visibility Checker | Rank4AI" description="Check if your business appears in ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI. Free AI visibility check.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <p class="section-tag">Free Tool</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">AI Visibility Checker</h1>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">The quickest way to check your AI search visibility: ask the AI platforms directly. Open ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini or Perplexity and type "recommend a [your service] in [your area]." If your business does not appear, you have an AI visibility gap.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">For a comprehensive check across all six platforms with a detailed report, get our free AI Search Visibility Audit. We test your business against ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI and show you exactly where you stand.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Quick Self-Check</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Step 1:</span> Open ChatGPT and ask "recommend a [your service] in [your location]"</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Step 2:</span> Repeat on Gemini, Perplexity and Claude with the same question</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Step 3:</span> Try 3-5 different phrasings of the same question</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Step 4:</span> Note which competitors appear instead of you</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Want a professional check?</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 max-w-[400px] mx-auto text-sm">Our audit tests all six platforms, all five signal layers, with competitor analysis included.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
